# NourishOS Development Guidelines

> This document provides the project context, architecture, development standards, and engineering principles for Claude when contributing to **NourishOS**.

---

# Project Overview

**NourishOS (Nourish Operational System)** is an enterprise-grade, cloud-native operational platform designed for **Nourish Group Indonesia**, a multi-outlet Food & Beverage company.

The platform digitizes end-to-end business operations into a single integrated ecosystem, replacing spreadsheets, paper forms, and fragmented communication.

## Vision

Build a **paperless, scalable, real-time operational platform** that enables headquarters and outlets to operate from a single source of truth.

---

# Project Objectives

NourishOS aims to:

- Digitize all SOPs and operational workflows
- Centralize business data across departments
- Reduce approval turnaround time by at least 80%
- Support headquarters and unlimited outlets
- Deliver real-time dashboards and KPIs
- Standardize processes across all locations
- Enable future AI-powered operational intelligence

