# Workflow Standards

All business processes follow the same lifecycle.

```
Draft

↓

Submitted

↓

Pending Approval

↓

Approved

↓

Completed
```

Alternative outcomes:

```
Rejected

Cancelled

Expired
```

Every state transition should:

- Create an Audit Log
- Trigger Notifications
- Generate Tasks (when applicable)

